title: Mini Mango
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Thai, Delivery, Take-out, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This restaurant was formed by the original creators of Sweet Mango in Edmonton. Mini has quality food with a quick self service format and a lower cost. Has an Asian Bistro look of design and decor. For vegetarians and vegans, they have expanded their veg offerings (marked with a V) and continue their practices of creating meals properly (even in a non 100% veg restaurant).
